==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Prolonged from [[ῥώομαι]] rhōomai (to dart; probably akin to  [[ῥύομαι]] {{GG|4506}}); 

===Pronunciation===
ῥώννυμι / rhōnnumi / hrone'-noo-mee

===Verb===
'''ῥώννυμι'''

# to [[strengthen]], that is, (imperative passive) have health (as parting exclamation, good bye): - [[farewell]].

